  "3042860": {
    "name": "Second Shift",
    "steam_appid": 3042860,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042860/extras/0ea695890793da01f49da50babc2511e.avif?t=1766061493\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042860/extras_big/0ea695890793da01f49da50babc2511e.avif?t=1766061493 width=800 height=208 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SECOND SHIFT</strong> 是一款第一人称恐怖游戏，让玩家沉浸在紧张压抑的氛围中。利用一座神秘的时钟，揭开可怕的秘密并尝试逃离矿井。解开谜题，注意周围细节，最重要的是——活下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042860/extras/5f9d4cdc8fa1c1c6bf3080bff7a778c6.poster.avif?t=1766061493\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042860/extras/5f9d4cdc8fa1c1c6bf3080bff7a778c6.webm?t=1766061493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在记者妻子死于一场可疑事故后，欧文·米勒潜入一家名为ZitanovaTech的神秘公司所运营的秘密矿区，寻求复仇。他意外发现了公司正在寻找的古老怀表。但这块表不仅能指引他前进，还释放出一个致命的存在。在挣扎求生的过程中，欧文逐渐揭开妻子死亡的真相以及公司隐藏的黑暗秘密。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>玩法</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>如果危险靠近，将光直接照向它。它可能会退缩……也许吧。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042860/extras/bdd63b6815a3438f6cfa834c2fe1d547.poster.avif?t=1766061493\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042860/extras/bdd63b6815a3438f6cfa834c2fe1d547.webm?t=1766061493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>砸碎、前进、继续……但你的镐很脆弱——最多只能破坏2块石头。</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042860/extras/4074bd563582a5760d82ea7327a65ac5.poster.avif?t=1766061493\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042860/extras/4074bd563582a5760d82ea7327a65ac5.webm?t=1766061493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>有些东西肉眼看不见。但钟表的光能让它们显现出来。</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042860/extras/7f35b7448c0a4abd543eddd7be77fb6b.poster.avif?t=1766061493\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042860/extras/7f35b7448c0a4abd543eddd7be77fb6b.webm?t=1766061493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这道光不仅能揭示秘密，也能照亮你的道路。小心使用……有冷却时间。</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042860/extras/4c2ee90c7a2c1fc3effaf1136a934a4b.poster.avif?t=1766061493\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042860/extras/4c2ee90c7a2c1fc3effaf1136a934a4b.webm?t=1766061493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>钟表能感知到接近的危险。如果它变红……做好准备。</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042860/extras/dcedca5bdb39f7e8e5b24a7bdc1ded85.poster.avif?t=1766061493\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042860/extras/dcedca5bdb39f7e8e5b24a7bdc1ded85.webm?t=1766061493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>面对潜伏在黑暗矿井深处的可怕怪物。准备好迎接恐惧的巅峰吧！</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042860/extras/961e156b46d834f1d311ef4e744735ec.poster.avif?t=1766061493\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042860/extras/961e156b46d834f1d311ef4e744735ec.webm?t=1766061493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
